free-scp-no-volunteers-fax-content =
    ██████████████████████████████████████████
    FOUNDATION INTERNAL COMMUNICATION
    CLASSIFICATION: LEVEL 4 / SITE DIRECTOR EYES ONLY
    ██████████████████████████████████████████

    TO:      Site Director, [REDACTED] Foundation Facility
    FROM:    O5 Oversight — Containment Division
    RE:      Anomalous Entity Containment Status — URGENT

    ──────────────────────────────────────────

    This communiqué is to formally notify site administration that as of the
    time of transmission, NO anomalous entities of any classification are
    currently confirmed active within your facility.

    Foundation monitoring systems have detected an absence of all tracked
    anomalies within the designated containment zones. Cross-referencing with
    recent breach reports, transfer logs, and neutralization records, our
    current assessment is as follows:

        • No Euclid-class entities detected within containment parameters.
        • No Keter-class entities detected within containment parameters.
        • No Safe-class entities requiring active supervision are present.

    ──────────────────────────────────────────

    ASSESSMENT:

    The cause of this absence has not yet been determined. Possible
    explanations under current investigation include, but are not limited to:

        1. Coordinated containment breach and subsequent self-relocation.
        2. Unauthorized removal by embedded hostile personnel.
        3. Systematic containment failure resulting in neutralization.
        4. Errors in monitoring equipment — engineering review recommended.

    ──────────────────────────────────────────

    DIRECTIVE:

    Site Director is advised to review all access logs, containment cell
    records, and personnel activity reports from the past 24 hours immediately.
    A full incident report must be submitted to O5 Oversight within 6 hours.

    Foundation High Command is monitoring the situation. Further instructions
    will follow pending your report.

    ██████████████████████████████████████████
    THIS MESSAGE WILL BE AUTOMATICALLY PURGED AFTER 12 HOURS
    UNAUTHORIZED DISTRIBUTION IS A CLASS-I INFRACTION
    ██████████████████████████████████████████
